extendedInfo.description: Ericsson Power ModulesThe Ericsson Power Modules application for Android brings the news on advanced board-mounted power solutions right into the palm of your hand.Stay tuned for the latest technologies, such as digital power control, to optimize power systems and reduce energy consumption.Get news updates from Ericsson Power Modules, or quickly find the nearest Ericsson representative, among many other features.Ericsson Power Modules is a world-class supplier of DC/DC power modules for distributed power architectures. Awarded for its leadership in innovative power technologies, Ericsson Power Modules has global design, development and manufacturing capabilities, in addition to a global sales network, to help its customers meet demands for high-performance and energy-efficient solutions.Learn more about Ericsson Power Modules at http://www.ericsson.com/powermodules

reviews.title: Great Job!
reviews.comment: Simple, fast and straight to the information I could expect from a supplier. I like very much the graphics and interfaces and looking forward for the next coming news. Keep the good job!
reviews.author: A Google User
